[SN]TITLE[SN]
Aaron Tshibola: Aston Villa sign midfielder from Reading in four-year deal

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Aston Villa have signed young Reading midfielder Aaron Tshibola on a four-year contract for an undisclosed fee.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 21-year-old Royals youth product played 17 times for the club since his Football League debut in a 4-0 defeat at Nottingham Forest in August 2014.
He made 23 league appearances in a half-season loan with League Two side Hartlepool United in 2014-15.
Tshibola will be reunited with former Royals boss Steve Clarke, who is now Villa's assistant manager.
